name: Trump Derangement Syndrome
description: Trump Derangement Syndrome is a mental condition in which a person has been driven effectively insane due to their dislike of Donald Trump. TDS has existed since 2015, this token is a representation of the new and revitalized memetics of another Trump Presidency. The election has been settled but the condition is now on the rise. Get diagnosed. This is a Four Year Meme. Launched with Pump.Fun on 11/07/2024
